      },
      "date": "2017-05-26 16:41:21.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nAndreas - This patch isn't related to interop testing. The problem is tests 9a and 9b are always being skipped for all versions of Lustre because the server version variable is never initialized. Since the server_version variable is empty these tests are being skipped for all versions of Lustre. \n\nThe code in this patch correctly gets and checks server version and the tests are now executed for master testing.",
